1
00:00:12,800 --> 00:00:13,679
(My name is Su Li.)

2
00:00:14,039 --> 00:00:15,000
(Pen name is Su Su.)

3
00:00:15,560 --> 00:00:17,239
(I am a journalist for Deep News.)

4
00:00:18,280 --> 00:00:20,239
(Some say my battlefield
is at the tip of my pen.)

5
00:00:20,600 --> 00:00:22,719
(But I'm more comfortable
walking the line of truth.)

6
00:00:23,600 --> 00:00:24,960
(Infiltrating pyramid
scheme headquarters,)

7
00:00:25,480 --> 00:00:26,960
(slipping through the drug zones
of Southeast Asia,)

8
00:00:27,640 --> 00:00:28,120
(disguising,)

9
00:00:28,559 --> 00:00:29,039
(tracking,)

10
00:00:29,440 --> 00:00:30,480
(adapting in close quarters.)

11
00:00:31,079 --> 00:00:32,719
(These are my weapons
for uncovering dark secrets.)

12
00:00:33,759 --> 00:00:35,000
(I have never feared the darkness.)

13
00:00:35,439 --> 00:00:36,920
(I answer only to facts and conscience.)

14
00:00:37,679 --> 00:00:38,320
(This time,)

15
00:00:38,600 --> 00:00:39,560
(I received a tip.)

16
00:00:40,159 --> 00:00:41,320
(Meiyan International Cosmetics)

17
00:00:41,320 --> 00:00:42,520
(Meiyan International Raw Materials)
(is suspected of raw material fraud.)

18
00:00:43,200 --> 00:00:44,840
(To tear apart this exquisite facade,)

19
00:00:45,359 --> 00:00:47,119
(I infiltrated a cosmetics factory
undercover.)

20
00:00:47,640 --> 00:00:48,840
(But I was attacked.)

21
00:00:51,560 --> 00:00:52,960
(Behind Meiyan International,)

22
00:00:53,200 --> 00:00:54,920
(an even greater conspiracy
must be lurking.)

23
00:00:55,479 --> 00:00:55,960
(Tonight,)

24
00:00:56,640 --> 00:00:57,359
(I must find a way into)

25
00:00:57,359 --> 00:00:59,079
(the Meiyan International
charity auction.)

26
00:00:59,520 --> 00:01:00,560
(From my informant,)

27
00:01:00,799 --> 00:01:01,880
(I will obtain the primary evidence.)

28
00:01:02,060 --> 00:01:05,620
=Inherently Kind=

29
00:01:05,700 --> 00:01:08,220
=Episode 1=
(The Same Face)

30
00:01:10,120 --> 00:01:10,640
Mrs. He,

31
00:01:11,000 --> 00:01:12,079
your seat is in the front row.

32
00:01:12,400 --> 00:01:12,959
This way, please.

33
00:01:13,359 --> 00:01:15,120
(Meiyan International Charity Auction)
Is that Hes' eldest daughter-in-law?

34
00:01:15,120 --> 00:01:16,359
(Gu Qingmei, Eldest Daughter-in-Law)
She came for her mother-in-law.

35
00:01:17,359 --> 00:01:19,319
She is originally the eldest daughter
of the Gu family.

36
00:01:19,480 --> 00:01:21,159
But unfortunately, she is
only the child of the first wife.

37
00:01:21,359 --> 00:01:23,159
Now the Gu family is run
by her younger brother.

38
00:01:23,319 --> 00:01:24,959
I heard they have already
cut her out of the Gu family.

39
00:01:24,959 --> 00:01:26,640
Ladies and gentlemen,

40
00:01:27,079 --> 00:01:28,840
please take your seats
in an orderly manner.

41
00:01:29,439 --> 00:01:31,760
(Su Li, News Journalist)
Our auction is about to begin.

42
00:01:33,480 --> 00:01:34,280
Mrs. He,

43
00:01:35,000 --> 00:01:37,120
did you have trouble finding your seat?

44
00:01:37,280 --> 00:01:38,439
(Is he confusing me with someone else?)

45
00:01:40,000 --> 00:01:40,519
Yes.

46
00:01:41,079 --> 00:01:42,519
May I take you there?

47
00:01:42,959 --> 00:01:43,680
No, no!

48
00:01:44,000 --> 00:01:44,760
I can manage on my own.

49
00:01:44,879 --> 00:01:45,519
Thank you.

50
00:01:45,840 --> 00:01:47,400
All proceeds from tonight's auction

51
00:01:47,599 --> 00:01:50,239
will be fully donated to charity
by Meiyan International.

52
00:01:50,719 --> 00:01:53,000
The starting bid for the first item
is three million.

53
00:01:54,439 --> 00:01:55,120
Four million.

54
00:01:55,480 --> 00:01:56,079
Five million.

55
00:01:56,599 --> 00:01:57,120
Eight million.

56
00:01:57,719 --> 00:01:58,519
Eight million.

57
00:01:59,439 --> 00:02:01,200
(These wealthy people
are really generous.)

58
00:02:01,400 --> 00:02:02,480
Eight million, going twice.

59
00:02:03,040 --> 00:02:04,120
Eight million, going three times.

60
00:02:04,200 --> 00:02:04,840
Sold.

61
00:02:06,480 --> 00:02:08,120
(Trying to send me to my death?)

62
00:02:08,400 --> 00:02:09,560
(You can't even mop properly!)

63
00:02:10,039 --> 00:02:12,680
(Even our dog is more useful than you.)

64
00:02:17,039 --> 00:02:17,720
This is our second item.

65
00:02:17,720 --> 00:02:18,680
(Platinum Diamond Necklace)
This is our second item.

66
00:02:18,680 --> 00:02:19,240
(Platinum Diamond Necklace)
Starting bid is six million.

67
00:02:19,240 --> 00:02:20,400
Starting bid is six million.

68
00:02:22,599 --> 00:02:23,840
(The jewelry has all been sold.)

69
00:02:24,439 --> 00:02:25,800
(Then find a way to get some more.)

70
00:02:32,439 --> 00:02:33,360
Ten million.

71
00:02:35,479 --> 00:02:37,159
This young lady has offered ten million.

72
00:02:43,039 --> 00:02:44,039
Ten million, going once.

73
00:02:45,120 --> 00:02:46,120
Ten million, going twice.

74
00:02:46,680 --> 00:02:48,280
(Almost forget my real purpose.)

75
00:02:48,680 --> 00:02:49,360
Sold.

76
00:02:50,319 --> 00:02:51,319
Congratulations to this young lady.

77
00:02:52,080 --> 00:02:52,800
Next item.

78
00:02:52,879 --> 00:02:53,360
Mrs. He.

79
00:02:53,360 --> 00:02:54,719
Starting bid is five million.

80
00:02:56,240 --> 00:02:56,800
Boss,

81
00:02:57,159 --> 00:02:58,560
the charity auction has begun.

82
00:02:59,639 --> 00:03:00,199
Find out

83
00:03:01,199 --> 00:03:02,960
what Meiyan International is hiding

84
00:03:04,000 --> 00:03:04,560
and

85
00:03:04,960 --> 00:03:06,000
last night

86
00:03:06,080 --> 00:03:08,080
who the woman was that
escaped from the cosmetics factory.

87
00:03:08,800 --> 00:03:09,479
Get down, get down.

88
00:03:10,080 --> 00:03:10,759
Quick, quick.

89
00:03:13,680 --> 00:03:14,159
Over there.

90
00:03:16,360 --> 00:03:17,319
They are from Meiyan International.

91
00:03:17,639 --> 00:03:18,240
Miss Su,

92
00:03:19,039 --> 00:03:20,159
all the documents are with me.

93
00:03:20,479 --> 00:03:22,000
Last night, I made an undercover visit
to the cosmetics factory.

94
00:03:22,080 --> 00:03:23,159
There are indeed major issues.

95
00:03:23,879 --> 00:03:25,280
If the evidence here proves true,

96
00:03:25,599 --> 00:03:26,719
it will be shocking.

97
00:03:27,039 --> 00:03:28,199
Please don't let anyone know
it came from me.

98
00:03:28,479 --> 00:03:28,960
I promise.

99
00:03:29,000 --> 00:03:29,479
Alright.

100
00:03:39,400 --> 00:03:41,599
(She looks just like me from behind.)

101
00:03:42,319 --> 00:03:44,479
(Am I hallucinating?)

102
00:04:00,319 --> 00:04:01,639
(Who is she exactly?)

103
00:04:22,000 --> 00:04:23,079
(Gu Qingmei?)

104
00:04:42,680 --> 00:04:43,600
Water.

105
00:04:52,180 --> 00:04:54,260
(He Jinchen; Eldest Son)

106
00:04:55,580 --> 00:04:57,180
(Xu Niannian; Second Daughter-in-Law)

107
00:04:58,580 --> 00:04:59,900
(He Jinxi; Third Daughter)

108
00:05:02,439 --> 00:05:03,879
(Madam He)
Finally awake?

109
00:05:04,160 --> 00:05:05,680
You seem to enjoy playing dead.

110
00:05:06,399 --> 00:05:08,319
(Who is this old lady?)

111
00:05:08,399 --> 00:05:11,040
Was making a spectacle at
the auction not enough for you?

112
00:05:11,120 --> 00:05:13,519
Now you're playing the victim.

113
00:05:14,720 --> 00:05:15,720
The reputation of He family

114
00:05:15,800 --> 00:05:17,279
has been completely ruined by you.

115
00:05:18,279 --> 00:05:19,720
Who are you people?

116
00:05:20,360 --> 00:05:21,519
And who am I?

117
00:05:22,560 --> 00:05:24,079
Did you lose your memory?

118
00:05:24,600 --> 00:05:25,959
This is more dramatic than a TV show.

119
00:05:26,360 --> 00:05:27,240
Really?

120
00:05:27,439 --> 00:05:28,839
I have never seen
an amnesia patient before.

121
00:05:30,240 --> 00:05:32,279
All of you are being so sarcastic.

122
00:05:33,199 --> 00:05:34,759
Is anyone going to say something useful?

123
00:05:34,800 --> 00:05:36,360
Don't play the fool here.

124
00:05:36,759 --> 00:05:38,519
Where did you hide the auction jewelry?

125
00:05:39,920 --> 00:05:42,079
These two pieces have good quality.

126
00:05:42,560 --> 00:05:43,720
But the price...

127
00:05:43,879 --> 00:05:44,759
We can talk about the price.

128
00:05:45,079 --> 00:05:45,800
I need cash.

129
00:05:46,319 --> 00:05:47,079
No problem.

130
00:05:47,279 --> 00:05:48,319
You are a regular customer.

131
00:05:52,759 --> 00:05:54,519
Are you not listening to me?

132
00:05:54,759 --> 00:05:55,879
Are you deaf?

133
00:05:58,279 --> 00:05:59,120
My nose!

134
00:05:59,199 --> 00:06:00,079
Mom, are you alright?

135
00:06:01,720 --> 00:06:02,639
Blood!

136
00:06:05,839 --> 00:06:06,600
Gu Qingmei.

137
00:06:07,560 --> 00:06:08,279
Are you insane?

138
00:06:08,800 --> 00:06:10,040
Look what you've done!

139
00:06:10,639 --> 00:06:11,600
Gu Qingmei?

140
00:06:13,360 --> 00:06:14,240
My name is Gu Qingmei?

141
00:06:14,600 --> 00:06:15,680
This is outrageous!

142
00:06:15,839 --> 00:06:16,759
You had the nerve to hit me!

143
00:06:16,839 --> 00:06:17,399
Mom.

144
00:06:20,600 --> 00:06:21,199
Miss Gu,

145
00:06:22,040 --> 00:06:23,160
your younger brother and stepmother

146
00:06:23,319 --> 00:06:24,879
passed away in a boating accident
last night.

147
00:06:25,000 --> 00:06:25,680
According to the will,

148
00:06:26,160 --> 00:06:27,199
you are now the sole legal heir

149
00:06:27,319 --> 00:06:28,360
of Gu Corporation.

150
00:06:43,079 --> 00:06:44,439
I need a ship to get out
of the country tonight.

151
00:06:44,560 --> 00:06:45,399
I must leave immediately.

152
00:06:47,319 --> 00:06:47,920
No problem.

153
00:07:04,199 --> 00:07:04,920
(Gu Qingmei,)

154
00:07:06,040 --> 00:07:07,800
(you will soon escape this cage)

155
00:07:08,839 --> 00:07:09,959
(and be reborn.)

156
00:07:11,600 --> 00:07:14,480
The patient shows significant
organic damage to the hippocampus.

157
00:07:15,040 --> 00:07:16,759
Suspected retrograde amnesia.

158
00:07:16,920 --> 00:07:18,759
We recommend rest at home for recovery.

159
00:07:20,879 --> 00:07:21,519
Impossible.

160
00:07:21,600 --> 00:07:22,720
Doctor, this is impossible!

161
00:07:22,879 --> 00:07:24,319
She was quite capable when she hit me.

162
00:07:24,680 --> 00:07:25,759
She is clearly faking it!

163
00:07:25,839 --> 00:07:27,079
She is clearly faking it!

164
00:07:27,279 --> 00:07:27,759
Mom,

165
00:07:28,439 --> 00:07:29,920
Her status has changed.

166
00:07:30,279 --> 00:07:31,160
Please calm down.

167
00:07:31,879 --> 00:07:32,720
We'll just wait and see.

168
00:07:34,199 --> 00:07:35,279
The affairs of the Gu family,

169
00:07:35,680 --> 00:07:36,439
I will handle them for you.

170
00:07:37,079 --> 00:07:38,040
Focus on your recovery.

171
00:07:39,040 --> 00:07:40,399
Anyway, you wouldn't be much help.

172
00:07:42,519 --> 00:07:43,160
Then...

173
00:07:44,040 --> 00:07:45,399
I leave it to you.

174
00:07:47,199 --> 00:07:48,199
Mom, let's go.

175
00:07:52,879 --> 00:07:54,360
(Car accident, amnesia.)

176
00:07:54,879 --> 00:07:56,120
(Wife of a wealthy family?)

177
00:07:56,480 --> 00:07:58,199
(Gu Qingmei)
(Heir to a corporation?)

178
00:07:58,199 --> 00:07:59,759
(Gu Qingmei)
(This is more absurd than a melodrama.)

179
00:08:21,720 --> 00:08:22,839
(So this is my home?)

180
00:08:23,680 --> 00:08:25,160
(My life must be on easy mode now.)

181
00:08:25,439 --> 00:08:26,040
Madam Gu,

182
00:08:26,120 --> 00:08:27,720
according to the rules,
we must disinfect you first.

183
00:08:28,160 --> 00:08:28,959
What are you doing?

184
00:08:33,759 --> 00:08:34,320
Give that to me.

185
00:08:36,399 --> 00:08:38,200
This rule isn't just for me, is it?

186
00:08:38,480 --> 00:08:39,720
Madam He set this rule.

187
00:08:40,000 --> 00:08:41,080
Then you are standing so close to me.

188
00:08:41,240 --> 00:08:42,200
You two should also be disinfected.

189
00:08:43,120 --> 00:08:43,559
Disinfect.

190
00:08:43,559 --> 00:08:44,399
Come on!

191
00:08:44,559 --> 00:08:45,240
No running away!

192
00:08:45,320 --> 00:08:45,919
Come, come.

193
00:08:45,960 --> 00:08:46,759
What's going on here?

194
00:08:47,320 --> 00:08:49,320
You cause chaos the moment you return.

195
00:08:49,639 --> 00:08:50,360
Madam He,

196
00:08:50,559 --> 00:08:52,080
Madam Gu is setting rules for us.

197
00:08:53,080 --> 00:08:53,960
Setting rules?

198
00:08:54,039 --> 00:08:55,559
The rules of He family

199
00:08:55,679 --> 00:08:57,679
aren't for a daughter-in-law to decide.

200
00:08:59,279 --> 00:09:00,200
Mom.

201
00:09:00,399 --> 00:09:02,240
I wouldn't dare to set rules.

202
00:09:05,840 --> 00:09:07,039
I am carrying germs on me.

203
00:09:07,120 --> 00:09:07,759
I just touched you.

204
00:09:07,879 --> 00:09:08,720
You must have been contaminated as well.

205
00:09:08,879 --> 00:09:09,440
Here.

206
00:09:09,559 --> 00:09:10,639
Let me disinfect you too.

207
00:09:10,759 --> 00:09:11,679
- Disinfect!
- You have gone too far!

208
00:09:11,799 --> 00:09:12,200
You...

209
00:09:14,679 --> 00:09:16,480
When did the He family have such a rule?

210
00:09:17,159 --> 00:09:17,960
Get out of my sight.

211
00:09:18,480 --> 00:09:18,960
Yes.

212
00:09:23,240 --> 00:09:24,399
You have truly gone too far.

213
00:09:29,080 --> 00:09:30,720
It seems the rules of the He family

214
00:09:31,320 --> 00:09:32,320
were made for me.

215
00:09:53,240 --> 00:09:54,120
You are home.

216
00:09:54,559 --> 00:09:55,559
You always stayed up waiting for me,

217
00:09:55,840 --> 00:09:57,080
no matter how late.

218
00:09:57,440 --> 00:09:58,320
What happened today?

219
00:09:58,960 --> 00:10:02,080
The medication made me drowsy.

220
00:10:10,159 --> 00:10:13,399
(My CEO husband is pretty fit!)

221
00:10:17,039 --> 00:10:17,879
(Tonight,)

222
00:10:18,759 --> 00:10:20,840
(is something going to happen?)

223
00:10:29,399 --> 00:10:29,960
(Here it comes.)

224
00:10:30,679 --> 00:10:31,399
(Here it comes!)

225
00:10:45,159 --> 00:10:46,399
(That's it?)

226
00:11:07,360 --> 00:11:08,080
Gu Qingmei!

227
00:11:08,639 --> 00:11:09,639
What are you doing?

228
00:11:10,480 --> 00:11:11,799
I... I don't know.

229
00:11:12,919 --> 00:11:13,679
Fine.

230
00:11:14,080 --> 00:11:15,360
You like playing amnesia, do you?

231
00:11:16,039 --> 00:11:17,279
You'd better play it
for the rest of your life.

232
00:11:23,039 --> 00:11:23,879
My foot...

233
00:11:25,039 --> 00:11:26,279
I thought we were husband and wife.

234
00:11:26,799 --> 00:11:28,159
What is going on with my body?

235
00:11:35,620 --> 00:11:38,220
(Mu Shaoze; Shareholder of Shengda)

236
00:11:43,240 --> 00:11:43,679
(Dad!)

237
00:11:44,759 --> 00:11:45,840
(My father is still in there!)

238
00:11:46,080 --> 00:11:46,720
(Let me go!)

239
00:11:47,080 --> 00:11:47,840
(Let me go!)

240
00:11:47,879 --> 00:11:48,639
(It's dangerous!)

241
00:11:48,759 --> 00:11:49,440
(Let me go!)

242
00:11:49,480 --> 00:11:50,320
(- Dad!
- You'll get yourself killed!)

243
00:11:50,960 --> 00:11:51,840
(Dad!)

244
00:11:55,720 --> 00:11:56,360
Boss,

245
00:11:56,399 --> 00:11:57,279
time is up.

246
00:12:00,720 --> 00:12:02,039
(My father's death)

247
00:12:02,279 --> 00:12:03,879
(is certainly connected
to the He family.)

248
00:12:05,039 --> 00:12:07,679
(Let's confront those monsters.)

249
00:12:29,500 --> 00:12:34,260
♪Time stole the proof of our love♪

250
00:12:34,260 --> 00:12:39,100
♪Hidden in the moonlight,
lost in the clouds♪

251
00:12:39,100 --> 00:12:43,660
♪Tangled glances and love fall together♪

252
00:12:43,660 --> 00:12:48,580
♪Into a spiral of thoughts,
memories rewinding♪

253
00:12:48,580 --> 00:12:52,380
♪Feelings both strange and familiar♪

254
00:12:52,380 --> 00:12:57,180
♪I just know you're
where my heart belongs♪

255
00:12:57,180 --> 00:13:00,020
♪Can't remember
when this flutter started♪

256
00:13:00,020 --> 00:13:02,700
♪Or how it's supposed to end♪

257
00:13:03,060 --> 00:13:08,620
♪Goodbye to the world rushing in♪

258
00:13:09,020 --> 00:13:15,820
♪Let me hide in your eyes
and never leave♪

259
00:13:16,100 --> 00:13:20,780
♪Feel the rhythm of your heartbeat♪

260
00:13:20,940 --> 00:13:27,740
♪Every tomorrow seems worth the wait♪

261
00:13:28,060 --> 00:13:34,860
♪Let me fill the emptiness of a century♪

262
00:13:35,060 --> 00:13:39,540
♪As the wind brushes past your hem♪

263
00:13:39,540 --> 00:13:42,900
♪All my hidden feelings come undone♪

264
00:13:42,900 --> 00:13:49,820
♪Right as I confess my love♪
